{
  "stem": "4693.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The-- later on, the refugees from Poland, they-- they were already a mixed group who migrated, wherever.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Somewhere in United States was not my dream country to go, I decided before the outbreak of the war that I would go to Australia.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I knew two things-- that they are racers in Melbourne, Melbourne Cup, and there is Bank of New South Wales in Sydney.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And that they establish a telegraph line, which reaches London so that they know the prices of wheat on the exchange in London.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This was my knowledge.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's like a wild west of the 18th century, or 19th century being in the United States.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's what I knew about.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] was studying.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was killing the time.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was engaged to a girl, who was one of the richest girls in Poland.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But we were interrupted.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We never married.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, I was working still with a solicitor.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But you had to go through it before you could sit for the exam.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were officially not completely closed.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was still some chance that you might go through it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I didn't have much choice.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You see, I was-- the family, my family was pretty assimilated-- part of it at least; part maybe was not so much.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "One of my cousins was, during the first World War head of the Polish underground in Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "My great, great grandfather was treasurer in 1863 of the Polish uprising against the Russians in Radom gubernias, maybe [? it was Kachka ?] gubernia.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] My great, great, great grandfather somewhere was the chief Rabbi of Warsaw, [?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Meisel, ?] who was a member of the national government in the uprising.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Look.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
